15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-299A of Title 63, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Oklahoma
20 Rural Hospitals Funding Assistance Grant Program Act of 2025".
21 B. There is hereby established the Oklahoma Rural Hospitals
22 Funding Assistance Grant Program.
